                        info.stakingRewards,
                        rewardAmount
                    ),
                    "StakingRewardsFactory::notifyRewardAmount: transfer failed"
                );
                StakingRewards(info.stakingRewards).notifyRewardAmount(
                    info.poolRewardToken[i],
                    rewardAmount
                );
            }
        }
